459
00:40:44,014 --> 00:40:46,160
Neko od vas mora izaći.
-Ja!

460
00:40:46,384 --> 00:40:48,842
Ne prekidaj me, Harold!
-Ja hoću da izaðem.

461
00:40:48,952 --> 00:40:52,099
